data.description: HOME ON THE RANGE!!!  LIKE THE LYRICS GO- "OH GIVE ME A HOME WHERE THE BUFFALO ROAM, WHERE THE DEER AND THE ANTELOPE PLAY" (WELL MAYBE NOT ANTELOPE- LOL). WELL, HERE IS THAT HOME- 6600 RIFLE RANGE ROAD!!! COME CHECK OUT THIS NICE 4 BEDROOM, 2 FULL BATHROOM HOME THAT'S SETTLED ON 1.27 ACRES OF WOODED LAND.  THE KITCHEN/DINING/LIVING AREA IS AN OPEN CONCEPT DESIGN AND ALL BEDROOMS ARE NICELY SIZED. THIS HOME IS ALREADY EQUIPPED WITH AN IN-GROUND STORM SHELTER THAT COULD HOLD UP TO EIGHT PEOPLE COMFORTABLE, A 10X12 STORAGE SHED, A BASKETBALL GOAL, STAINLESS STEEL REFRIGERATOR, RECENTLY PURCHASED HOTWATER TANK AND A WASHER/DRYER SET.  IF YOU ARE WANTING TO FEEL LIKE YOU ARE IN THE COUNTRY WHILE IN THE CITY LIMITS THIS IS THE PLACE TO BE. THERE'S PLENTY OF OUTDOOR SPACE TO ADVENTURE. WHO KNOWS YOU JUST MAY SEE A DEER PLAYING- AND POSSIBLY- ONE OR TWO BUFFALO ROAMING.  AND FOR THOSE WHO WANT A HOME WITH A WHITE PICKET FENCE (GOT YOU-THIS ONE HAS ONE!!).  SO, IF YOU WOULD LIKE A HOME ON THE (RIFLE) RANGE ACT NOW!!  PLEASE CONTACT YOUR FAVORITE REALTOR OR ME TO SCHEDULE YOUR VIEWING!!
